data.description: Welcome to this desired NW community home. This gorgeous single story home features an open-floor plan with 3 bed, 2 bath, an office and  a formal dinning room/family room. This Gem has new tile flooring, new baseboards, new paint,  beautiful dark cabinets, granite counters, an island with sink and breakfast bar,perfect for hosting. As you walk to the master bedroom you will find a large walk in closet, a master bathroom with double sinks, a separate shower and soaking tub for relaxation. This home has very unique features including a 3 car garage with Epoxy flooring and a covered back patio. It includes a front porch for those perfect mornings to sit down, relax, and enjoy your coffee. This home features a greatly landscaped backyard with producing fruit trees. You don't want to miss out on this home! Schedule your showing today!
